{"tid":709483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父親節11歲男生尼龍繩纏頸 延至昨晚7時22分逝世","createTime":"2018-06-20T04:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T10:45:53.000Z","uid":41404,"like":48,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"dca4d2f8cc049ab89771f062e9f92f79f546f914","tid":709483,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"父親節早上在將軍澳日出康城緻藍天晶巒寓所，遭尼龍繩纏頸命危的11歲潘姓男生，在聯合醫院經過與死神搏鬥三天後，最終昨晚（19號）7時22分不幸離世，家人獲悉噩耗悲慟不已。<br />\n<br />\n本月17日早上9時許，42歲潘父發現兒子在寓所內遭尼龍繩纏頸，疑似上吊。父親急忙把他解下及報警，救援人員接報到場時，男童已陷入昏迷，經搶救後再轉至聯合醫院兒童深切治療部留醫，情況危殆，延至昨晚辭世。<br />\n消息稱，11歲男生讀小學五年級，品學兼優，家庭背景正常，近日亦無透露輕生之念，據了解，潘氏參加了童軍，近日正學習繩結的知識，包括如何打繩結及如何解除，故警方關注今次勒頸事故會否有可能是有人學習繩結包括如何解困期間不慎發生意外所致。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180620/58340463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180620%2F58340463&d=GMefUb1EwwwOqWogq8hO054f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a48b2c2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180620%2F58340463&h=95519660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180620/58340463</a>"},{"pid":"f6371688591c3c4272ead95f5cbed3f2180ccc38","tid":709483,"uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:43:49.000Z","msg":"日出康城11歲男童 家中吊頸昏迷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/705279/page/2?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/705279/page/2?ref=ios</a>"},{"pid":"da723ae088d9c144e09b7665b27f15dedde15abd","tid":709483,"uid":53378,"like":3,"dislike":48,"score":-45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"潘氏參加了童軍，近日正學習繩結的知識，包括如何打繩結及如何解除，故警方關注今次勒頸事故會否有可能是有人學習繩結包括如何解困期間不慎發生意外所致。<br />\n<br />\n......"},{"pid":"f359c9804955733512e8ddee8cf00df0c67e3f44","tid":709483,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":36,"score":-35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:44:04.000Z","msg":"係咪時候開始立法實名買刀同買繩了"},{"pid":"e2bc3bed6bfebdb9ad1a48f954d9228e928a78e9","tid":709483,"uid":21917,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:46:12.000Z","msg":"童軍會教到人自己勒頸？"},{"pid":"32d949e8234c4a2bd052e6d9207cf4dc39e264e9","tid":709483,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:50:00.000Z","msg":"將軍澳一名11歲男生，在本周日（17日）父親節，於日出康城緻藍天晶巒寓所被尼龍繩纏頸狀似自縊，被姓潘(42歲)父親揭發報警。潘童被解下送院搶救，情況一直危殆，在與死神搏鬥3日，延至昨(19日)晚上7時22分離世，家人傷心欲絕。 <br />\n<br />\n消息指，潘就讀小學五年級，成績優秀和品行良好，家庭生活美滿，事前他毫無異樣，亦沒有遺書，最近他正學習童軍繩結法，故警方正循意外抑或自殺展開調查。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180620/mobile/bkn-20180620111611693-0620_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180620%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180620111611693-0620_00822_001.html&d=GMefUb1EwwwOqWogq8hO054f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=196bd47f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180620/mobile/bkn-20180620111611693-0620_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"df4229f92eadd89a4f0db4a4ff52c1781eb48e75","tid":709483,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:00:46.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"22722eba88a9474b44f1f3a1123b356948864558","tid":709483,"uid":34410,"like":64,"dislike":4,"score":60,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:02:16.000Z","msg":"今次做乜冇人屌童軍教壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf844e2bffd5e46edd76132d2caa8f93c3f5f3f","tid":709483,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c5743472c1e96bb8d12262c8b5ab7080ec3b10","tid":709483,"uid":4880,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:05:57.000Z","msg":"又品學兼優"},{"pid":"9e8ea9c79940a00bf82ed7485d42f9449bfcecd5","tid":709483,"uid":51701,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"22722eb